message:
Frontend plugins working (No relations between them)

* Now you can create plugins that extend frontend,
  add the next folder inside you plugins and work
  as if you was working on nextjs vanila.

  PS: All the files (except pages ones) must be stored
  under src/, for accessing them, just refer to
  '@pluginName/path/to/file/from/src'

* A new example is being developed
  The new example uses all the power of a plugin (controllers, services
  and front)
  * You can test the login in {{URL}}/user-admin/login

TODO:
  Plugins
    Make the plugins interact in the frontend
    Let you choose custom routes on front
    Plugins permissions
    Run plugins on VM
    Let you extend _app.js, _document.js, etc

  CLI
    Better dev mode

  leemons-database
    Expose transactions on leemons.query
